                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17891028-49-defend495 t17891028-49-punish245"></join>
               Transported for seven years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the second Middlesex Jury before Mr. Justice HEATH.</p>
